<h1><%=age_group.description%> Age Group - <%=age_group.day%></h1>
<% if exhibition %>
<p>The <%=age_group.description%> Tournament will follow the FA's guidelines for non competitive tournaments for this
    age.
</p>
<p>Therefore the <%=age_group.description%> tournament will be an exhibition only event.</p>
<br/>
<p>All participants will receive a commemorative medal.</p>

<% if team == 'U6' %>
    <br/>
    <p>The U6 age group will also play 7-a-side mini soccer instead of 5 a-side.</p>
<% end %>

<div>
    <br/>

    <p>Teams that have completed registration are listed below.</p><br/>
    <% teams.each do |team| %>
        <div style="padding-left:40px;">
            <p><%= team.name team.designation %></p>
        </div>
    <% end %>
</div>